{"tid":748973,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動物朋友たつき監督內幕 [含撚朋友]","createTime":"2018-07-19T15:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T17:26:49.000Z","uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f27a27324a70247840cdc135f65a15d9cbe3256","tid":748973,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/233130_d39bfe49986d90dbef5ccee9ada48739.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F233130_d39bfe49986d90dbef5ccee9ada48739.jpg&h=e7d513f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n動物朋友即將推出新作 原創短篇動畫《歡迎來到傑帕力公園》8/12開始配信<br />\n<br />\n舊監督たつき被換掉 一堆網民在屌角川 炎上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正原因竟然係たつき監督搶了吉崎的風采 <br />\n一講動物朋友就諗起たつき監督 唔係人物原創者吉崎觀音<br />\n喧賓奪主搞到吉崎不爽<br />\n搵左一個幫自己含撚既刷鞋仔擔任新監督<br />\n<br />\n含撚刷鞋仔 春日森春木<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/233031_e3f19d4ead2b258e9c9e7d9450163e12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F233031_e3f19d4ead2b258e9c9e7d9450163e12.jpg&h=49464c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nスタッフ<br />\n       <br />\n原作：けものフレンズプロジェクト<br />\nコンセプトデザイン：吉崎観音<br />\nシリーズ構成・脚本：釼持竜太郎<br />\nゲーム版シナリオ製作：フロンティアクリエイターズプロジェクト<br />\nシナリオプロデューサー：栗田真樹生<br />\n音響監督：阿部信行<br />\n音楽：立山秋航、松野恭平<br />\nプロデューサー：細谷伸之、梶井斉、加藤英治<br />\nキャスティング：池沢勝斗<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">監督・脚本・動画・撮影・編集：春日森春木</span></span><br />\n企画：けものフレンズプロジェクト<br />\n協力：ネクソン<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條刷鞋者 之前已經做過keroro軍曹<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">監督・脚本・動画・撮影・編集を務めるのは、フラッシュアニメ「ケロロ ～keroro～」などを手がけてきた春日森春木。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吉崎観音自己冇料到 手機game執7<br />\n人地たつき動畫搞起左套野  套野紅左<br />\n佢就批鬥 換走監督 換自己人頂個位<br />\n業界黑暗"},{"pid":"f22590aa4868a0ee6bc264f0f4eaae9a4a01807f","tid":748973,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"第二季狗都唔𨳒"},{"pid":"dba8e1947b0c42c2cbbc4e00bf9f1aeec3dc6c1d","tid":748973,"uid":1972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"動畫啲樣同佢本身個人設嘅樣都唔同啦"},{"pid":"4b7ac1ee52a28fd60e0532aec0cfe974f15c3caa","tid":748973,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f22590aa4868a0ee6bc264f0f4eaae9a4a01807f","tid":748973,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"第二季狗都唔𨳒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"睇下搞到咩把戲<br />\n<br />\n       <br />\nラッキービースト：内田　彩<br />\nミライ：内田　彩<br />\nサーバル：野中　藍<br />\nナレーション：尾崎由香<br />\n<br />\n冇背包都有內田 ま..あや <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699366a5bc8fc1361891590d119d24df8e2f06f9","tid":748973,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b558dc6880303715830471d17a9219a911af80a","tid":748973,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"咁u質文章都冇人理<br />\n<br />\n圍爐膠po 就熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a718fe3f87fd5e835188bd2fbc062dc4f192f13","tid":748973,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:26:49.000Z","msg":"過氣朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}